comments.body:
This may happen when you are on Windows or copy source code from Windows.
To verify this, please make sure file "storm-core/src/dev/resources/storm.rb"(another file is storm.py) is a symbol link. If it is not, you need to use git to download fresh code on Linux.

thanks a lot.I follow your suggestions,and use git to download code and compile,the above error has disappeared. But the below errors are born,is it normal? and what's the problem? thanks in advance.
